<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269265>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Neokodaiana minensis Meng & Qin, sp. nov., holotype. A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, lateral view. C. Frons and clypeus. D. Head and thorax, latero-ventral view. E. Male anal tube and pygofer, lateral view. F. Capitulum of style, dorsal view. G. Gonapophyses IX and gonaspiculum bridge, right view. H. Male anal tube, dorsal view. I. Connective. J. Penis, lateral view. Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269265/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269266>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Neokodaiana minensis Meng & Qin, sp. nov., holotype. A. Tegmen. B. Hind wing. C. Penis, apical half, ventral view. D. Penis, left view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269266/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.269267>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Neokodaiana minensis Meng & Qin, sp. nov. A. Female anal tube, dorsal view. B. Gonoplac, lateral view. C. Gonoplac, dorsal view. D. Gonapophyses IX and gonaspiculum bridge, dorsal view. E. Gonapophyses IX and gonaspiculum bridge, right view. F. Sternum VII, ventral view. G. Gonocoxa VIII and gonapophysis VIII, right view. Scale bars = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/269267/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

